 Someone on my server did an awesome web-based thing. You put in class. Then you enter values for the different stats. Pick a slot. And it will give you a list of the best items there are for you for that slot. In order, stats listed, based on your stat preference. I'd post a link, but not sure they want, or can handle, the added traffic.<br>
<br>
 Anyhoo those are the values I enter in for it. And it's about 95% accurate on what item I would personally pick for every slot. Numbers = points. And whatever item has the most points is the top rated one. Etc etc. Keep in mind my numbers are for me. Someone comfortably over the soft cap, and now finally well over 205stam. This is what it gives me if I put in those values for ear slot.<br>
<br>
1. 85 Lizard Bone Earring (AC:2, Sta:10, Agi:6, Dex:6, Chr:5, Mana:35, HP:70, DR:5, PR:5) <br>
2. 81 Vyrinn's Earring of Insanity (AC:25, Str:15, Sta:12, HP:50, MR:5, CR:5, FR:5, DR:5, PR:5) <br>
3. 75 Mosquito Leg Earring (AC:8, Sta:7, HP:65, DR:7) <br>
4. 73 Essence Pearl (Str:10, Wis:10, Int:10, HP:65, MR:7, CR:7, FR:7, DR:7, PR:7) <br>
5. 49 Spiderfang Earring (AC:7, Agi:7, Dex:7, Mana:30, HP:35) <br>
6. 47 Earring of Pain (AC:6, Wis:5, Int:5, Sta:10, HP:35, MR:5, DR:5, PR:5) <br>
7. 46 Earring of Quirkiness (AC:6, Str:4, Wis:4, Int:4, Sta:4, Agi:4, Dex:4, Chr:4, Mana:35, HP:35) <br>
8. 42 Pearly Sarnak Bangle (AC:2, Sta:10, HP:35, DR:5, PR:5) <br>
9. 39 Yunnb's Earring (AC:2, Wis:15, Int:15, Mana:50, HP:35, CR:5, FR:10, Wgt:0.1) <br>
10. 36 Black Sapphire Electrum Earring (AC:2, Mana:25, HP:35) <br>
